data.description: This full brick four bedroom home offers ample space for family members or guests. The large master bedroom has two separate walk in closets and the master bath has separate tub and shower. The two other bathrooms ensure convenience and privacy for everyone. The crown molding adds an elegant touch throughout the interior.  This well-equipped and spacious home is a strong contender for a growing family seeking comfort and functionality. The roof, HVAC and water heater are all less than a year old. If you're interested, be sure to arrange a showing to get a closer look at the property and assess if it meets your family's needs and preferences.
